# 🏗️ SmartEstate-AI: 3D Property Intelligence

A cutting-edge Real Estate landing page that integrates **Google Model-Viewer** for 3D architectural visualization and an **AI-driven Assistant** for property analysis.

## 🚀 Core Features
- **Interactive 3D Viewport**: Full 360° rotation and zoom of building models.
- **AI Virtual Assistant**: A floating chat interface designed to answer structural and financial queries.
- **Smart Insights**: AI-calculated yield estimates and thermal efficiency ratings.
- **Responsive Design**: Built with Tailwind CSS for mobile and desktop optimization.

## 🛠️ Technology Stack
- **3D Engine**: [Google <model-viewer>](https://modelviewer.dev/)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS (PostCSS)
- **Intelligence**: Integrated Chat UI (Ready for OpenAI/Gemini API)

